dct_description_sm: Map of China showing provinces, rivers, towns and with relief shown pictorially. Includes a table of chinese words translated into french. Plate 22 from: Atlas universel : pour servir a l'etude de la geographie et de l'histoire anciennes et modernes. Paris : Desenne & Menard, 1834. In French.
Ames Library of South Asia Maps
